  "text": "In Fig. 1 , recoveries of DQ or DQH 2 in the cell medium at the end of the 30-min incubations were less than the initial measured concentrations. Previous studies showed that DQ, but not DQH 2 , associates nonspecifically in a first-order manner with the spectrophotometric cuvettes [CITATION_1] . Taking this binding into consideration, on average Ͼ98% of the DQ or DQH 2 initially measured in the medium could be accounted for as DQ plus DQH 2 at the end of the 30-min incubation periods (see Data analysis and Ref. [CITATION_2] ).",
